desc: 测试批量插入员工表，测试点，批量执行，自动生成主键ID
name: InsertStaffBatch

oqls.name: InsertStaffBatchVars
oqls.oql: insert into Staff(staffCode, staffName, joinDate, departDate, descr, status, creator) values (#{staffCode}, #{staffName}, #{joinDate}, #{departDate}, #{descr}, #{status}, #{creator})
oqls.sql: insert into STAFF(STA_CODE, STA_NAME, JOIN_DATE, DEPART_DATE, DESCR, STATUS, CREATOR_NAME, CREATOR_KEY) values (#{staffCode}, #{staffName}, #{joinDate}, #{departDate}, #{descr}, #{status}, #{creator.name}, #{creator.key})
